    "description": "Ecom Express invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Marketplace Manager at our Ghaziabad location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Ecom Express:\nEcom Express is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Referral bonus program\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ghaziabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Ecom Express!",
